'''Neurosarcoidosis''' is involvement of the [[brain]] with [[Sarcoidosis]]. It may be treated with Corticosteroids<ref>http://www.ninds.nih.gov/disorders/neurosarcoidosis/neurosarcoidosis.htm</ref> including [[Prednisone]].
